      "category": "sectors",
      "subcategory": "software",
      "summary": "The AI model layer is dominated by an Anthropic–OpenAI duopoly, with both labs experiencing rapid ARR growth driven by agent workflows and enterprise adoption. Chinese model vendors are accelerating, but competition is intensifying, as evidenced by Anthropic's accusations against Alibaba's Qwen AI lab for illicitly accessing its frontier models.",
